-- Apple's older iPad 2 now sells for $399
-- 
-- Wed Mar 7, 2012 3:24pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/03/07/us-apple-discount-idUSTRE8261UZ20120307

 

 SAN FRANCISCO  (Reuters) - Apple Inc slashed the price on the iPad 2 to $399, minutes after announcing that its third-generation tablet hits store shelves next week. 
 CEO Tim Cook revealed details of the company's third-generation, 4G-ready tablet on Wednesday at a tightly scripted event in downtown San Francisco. (Reporting By  Poornima Gupta  and Alexei Oreskovic)